# Example: Crawl one radio-related site into generated/radio-comms.zim and register it locally

name: Radio & Mesh Communications
description: Meshtastic documentation
tags: [radio-comms, networking-mesh]
depth: comprehensive

sites:
  - url: https://meshtastic.org/docs
    scope: prefix
    page_limit: 1000

defaults:
  size_limit_mb: 512
  timeout_minutes: 60
